keystream_block(input16) = E(input16) = L( N(input) )  where N applies per-byte bijection N_j to byte j, L affine.

Let y_j = N_j(input_j)  in GF(2)^8. Then E(input) = M * (y_0||...||y_15) + c, where M is 128x128 GF(2) matrix, c constant. Actually L includes the final per-round keys folded into c, and ShiftRows/MixColumns into M.

